high_descs: Turn left, turn left at the fridge, and walk to the sink.
Pick up the yellow cup from the left side of the sink.
Put the cup down in the right side of the sink.
Move to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the left side of the sink.
Move to face the right side of the sink.
Put the knife in the yellow cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move a yellow cup to the sink and put a knife in the yellow cup.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink on the left.
Pick up the orange glass from the left side of the sink.
Put the orange glass into the right side of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife to the left of the spoon on the left side of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the knife inside the orange cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass and a knife in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the cup from the left side of the sink.
Put the cup in the right side of the sink.
Go back to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the left side of the sink.
Go back to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife in the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it in the sink.
